---
// src/components/VisiMisi.astro
---
<section id="visimisi" class="py-15 bg-slate-50 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(#e2e8f0_1px,transparent_1px)] [bg-size:20px_20px] opacity-40"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-950 mb-4 tracking-tight">PERHIPTANI DPD KABUPATEN SRAGEN</h2>
            <div class="w-100 h-1 bg-yellow-500 mx-auto mt-2 mb-6 rounded-full"></div>
            <h4 class="text-slate-600 text-2xl leading-relaxed">
                Adalah Organisasi Berazaskan Pancasila, Berbasis Keilmuan, Keahlian, Persaudaraan, Kemasyarakatan, Kemandirian, dan Tidak Berafiliasi dengan Organisasi Politik.
            </h4>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 items-start">
            <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 border-l-8 border-blue-900 relative group hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300 flex flex-col h-full">
                <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition pointer-events-none">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-24 h-24 text-blue-900" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z"/></svg>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 ml-5">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">Visi Kami</h3>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex-grow flex items-center">
                    <blockquote class="text-slate-600 text-xl leading-relaxed italic border-l-4 border-slate-200 pl-6 py-2">
                        "Terwujudnya penyuluh pertanian yang profesional, kompeten, dan mampu mensejahterakan petani melalui pertanian yang maju, mandiri, dan berkelanjutan."
                    </blockquote>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/50 border-l-8 border-green-600 relative group hover:-translate-y-2 transition duration-300 flex-col h-full">
                <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
                     <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-24 h-24 text-green-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z"/></svg>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 ml-5">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">Misi Organisasi</h3>
                </div>
                
                <ul class="space-y-1">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-50 transition duration-300 cursor-default group/item">
                        <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-green-200 group-hover/item:scale-110 transition duration-300">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Mengembangkan sistem penyuluhan pertanian yang efektif, efisien, dan produktif.</span>
                    </li>
                    
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-50 transition duration-300 cursor-default group/item">
                         <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-green-200 group-hover/item:scale-110 transition duration-300">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Mengembangkan serta menyebarluaskan ilmu, teknologi, metode, dan manajemen penyuluhan pertanian.</span>
                    </li>
                    
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-50 transition duration-300 cursor-default group/item">
                         <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-green-200 group-hover/item:scale-110 transition duration-300">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Membina jiwa korsa, mengembangkan profesionalisme, dan menyalurkan aspirasi penyuluh pertanian.</span>
                    </li>

                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-green-50 transition duration-300 cursor-default group/item">
                         <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1 shadow-md shadow-green-200 group-hover/item:scale-110 transition duration-300">
                            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">Mendukung program pemerintah dalam mencapai swasembada pangan dan meningkatkan pendapatan petani.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>